column5: The C.C on the PM,S.  My fingers are sore.

Highlight... right click.. copy. Next.. right click.. paste ! lol Yep.. PITA for arranging a multi person gathering, but a spam issue the mods had to nip in the butt!  Oh.. and BTW.. I didnt' get a Merry Christmas PM from ya. Guess your fingers got toooo tired......
YA LIE. Lump of coal for you.
LOL.. now I do, thought I'd be left off your "card" list !
I got mine thanks Brian then I sent you and Wayne a deer hunting tip...  Can you get your e-mails from work ?
No Norm,Im on parole.  Wayne,forward that to me will ya.
